(Samshin)
When a person's handprints or blood are on an object,
if a wish dwells within it,

4
00:01:03,813 --> 00:01:05,732
it becomes a goblin.

5
00:01:09,110 --> 00:01:11,112
[A SIGNIFICANT SOUND EFFECT]

6
00:01:13,073 --> 00:01:16,451
In numerous battlefields,
thousands of blood-stained swords

7
00:01:16,534 --> 00:01:17,994
[THE SKY RUMBLES]

8
00:01:18,078 --> 00:01:21,164
Since it has been stained with the blood of its owner,
how much more?

9
00:01:25,502 --> 00:01:27,587
[DREAMLIKE MUSIC]

10
00:01:37,305 --> 00:01:40,266
[Tire screeching sound]
Only the goblin bride

11
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,769
will draw that sword.

12
00:01:44,020 --> 00:01:48,316
When the sword is drawn, it will return to nothing and find peace

13
00:01:58,284 --> 00:02:01,538
(Samshin)
It could only be a wicked prophecy

14
00:02:03,373 --> 00:02:06,334
Thus, the goblin who was awakened to immortality

15
00:02:07,001 --> 00:02:10,463
is everywhere in this world
and nowhere at all

16
00:02:10,672 --> 00:02:11,631
Even now, somewhere...

17
00:02:11,714 --> 00:02:14,175
[LAUGHTER]

18
00:02:15,218 --> 00:02:17,137
Why are you laughing, you rotten thing?

19
00:02:18,555 --> 00:02:21,391
(Yeonhee)
'Even now, somewhere,
I'm looking for my bride'

20
00:02:21,474 --> 00:02:23,935
'That bride is me' Is that what you mean?

21
00:02:24,018 --> 00:02:25,061
[LAUGHTER]

22
00:02:25,937 --> 00:02:29,232
Though I may seem like this,
in my youth, I made many men cry.

23
00:02:29,315 --> 00:02:30,233
(Yeonhee)
Tch

24
00:02:30,316 --> 00:02:33,027
I came here for no reason again,
don't be surprised where that old hag went.

25
00:02:33,111 --> 00:02:34,904
Hmm, I'm envious

26
00:02:36,698 --> 00:02:38,366
(Samshin)
I’m the one who’s senile.

27
00:02:38,449 --> 00:02:40,702
It's not something to brag about in front of a single mother.

28
00:02:42,370 --> 00:02:44,330
Tch, how cruel.

29
00:02:44,831 --> 00:02:46,875
(Sanshin)
Lower the price of spinach, lower the price of cabbage.

30
00:02:46,958 --> 00:02:48,251
What’s wrong with me?

31
00:02:49,002 --> 00:02:51,421
That bastard who left you is the one who's bad.

32
00:02:52,130 --> 00:02:53,006
[THE DISAPPROVING BREATH OF SANSHIN]

33
00:02:53,965 --> 00:02:55,300
Well, that’s true.

34
00:02:55,383 --> 00:02:56,301
[SHE SMILES LIGHTLY]

35
00:02:57,135 --> 00:02:58,803
But that story is really sad.

36
00:02:59,012 --> 00:03:01,264
(Sanshin)
[scoffing]
It’s plenty sad.

37
00:03:01,347 --> 00:03:03,641
It’s an extremely romantic curse.

38
00:03:04,225 --> 00:03:06,394
That you have to find a bride to die.

39
00:03:08,563 --> 00:03:09,856
(Yeonhee)
God is cruel.

40
00:03:10,023 --> 00:03:12,275
(Three Gods)
The gods were originally bad

41
00:03:12,442 --> 00:03:14,861
Selfish and full of jealousy

42
00:03:15,695 --> 00:03:17,113
Only knowing themselves, just themselves

43
00:03:19,824 --> 00:03:21,743
They're just the same as any other guy

44
00:03:23,077 --> 00:03:26,205
(Yeonhee)
Ah, I'm going to leave now, have a lot of sales

45
00:03:26,414 --> 00:03:28,541
