132
00:09:01,791 --> 00:09:03,918
Kim Shin, lay down your armor and follow the imperial decree.

133
00:09:07,129 --> 00:09:08,130
(Subordinate)
You rascal!

134
00:09:09,006 --> 00:09:10,341
Try saying that again.

135
00:09:10,424 --> 00:09:12,176
You, a mere seventh rank fellow,

136
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:13,553
dare to speak of the general's name...

137
00:09:13,636 --> 00:09:15,179
The returning army's accompaniment, Kim Shin!

138
00:09:15,263 --> 00:09:16,138
[TENSE MUSIC]

139
00:09:16,222 --> 00:09:17,932
- (Soldier 1) Lay down your armor
- (Subordinate) Truly...

140
00:09:20,101 --> 00:09:21,102
I heard it

141
00:09:21,727 --> 00:09:22,728
Wait

142
00:09:36,409 --> 00:09:37,451
Is it done?

143
00:09:38,286 --> 00:09:39,912
The traitor Kim Shin

144
00:09:39,996 --> 00:09:42,623
(Soldier 1)
Kneel with your sword in your mouth and follow the imperial decree.

145
00:09:42,707 --> 00:09:44,500
I will pull out your tongue!

146
00:09:44,625 --> 00:09:46,210
(Subordinate)
A traitor, you say?

147
00:09:46,294 --> 00:09:48,713
Are you insane? Have you gone mad?

148
00:09:51,090 --> 00:09:53,175
[People murmur]
[Angry breaths of the subordinate]

149
00:09:58,556 --> 00:09:59,515
General

150
00:09:59,599 --> 00:10:02,768
(Soldier 1)
The traitor Kim Shin
with a sword in his mouth, kneel...

151
00:10:04,061 --> 00:10:06,230
[HEAVY MUSIC]

152
00:10:06,981 --> 00:10:08,816
I wish to see His Majesty, clear the way

153
00:10:09,900 --> 00:10:12,612
- The sinner Kim Shin...
- If you block the way, you will surely die.

154
00:10:13,446 --> 00:10:14,530
(Kim Shin)
Clear the way.

155
00:10:15,489 --> 00:10:16,490
[The arrow flies swiftly]
[The soldier's groan]

156
00:10:16,574 --> 00:10:18,159
[Arrows are pouring down]
[People's screams]

157
00:10:24,165 --> 00:10:25,750
[THE GROANS OF SOLDIERS]

158
00:10:29,211 --> 00:10:30,796
(Commoner 2)
Please save me, please save me

159
00:10:33,174 --> 00:10:34,550
(Commoner 2)
Please save me

160
00:10:34,634 --> 00:10:35,718
[THE SCREAMS OF THE COMMONERS]

161
00:10:35,801 --> 00:10:37,053
[A SUBORDINATE SHOUTS]

162
00:10:37,136 --> 00:10:38,679
(Subordinate)
You bastards!

163
00:10:39,013 --> 00:10:42,642
In the name of the lord,
we have fought for three days and nights

164
00:10:42,725 --> 00:10:45,853
This is the path of returning alive
from that hell on earth

165
00:10:45,936 --> 00:10:50,191
Yet you guys, how dare you!

166
00:10:50,274 --> 00:10:52,943
(Jungheon)
Open the gates!

167
00:11:00,034 --> 00:11:01,035
[THE GATES SWING OPEN]

168
00:11:01,118 --> 00:11:02,411
Guard them

169
00:11:04,163 --> 00:11:05,247
I will be back soon

170
00:11:38,823 --> 00:11:42,576
The king above the subjects, the god above the king

171
00:11:42,660 --> 00:11:45,413
That god is said to refer to Kim Shin

172
00:11:48,666 --> 00:11:50,584
[HEAVY MUSIC]

173
00:11:53,504 --> 00:11:56,674
(Chunghun)
The author's endless victory announcements
enchant the people

174
00:11:56,757 --> 00:12:00,177
As the author's power repeatedly mocks the royal family

175
00:12:00,261 --> 00:12:04,056
May the national laws strictly govern it

176
00:12:07,476 --> 00:12:11,313
(Kim Shin)
He saw the enemy's blades clearly

177
00:12:12,189 --> 00:12:15,526
But he could not see
the young king's
jealousy and fear directed at him

178
00:12:18,696 --> 00:12:19,697
That was

179
00:12:21,449 --> 00:12:24,368
the sharpest blade aimed
at himself.

180
00:12:27,705 --> 00:12:29,123
He did not know

181
00:12:36,964 --> 00:12:38,924
Are you really going to go this far?

182
00:12:39,008 --> 00:12:41,719
(Young King)
So don't come any closer, stop

183
00:12:42,136 --> 00:12:44,597
Whatever it is, stop

184
00:12:45,181 --> 00:12:47,141
Stop there and die a traitor

185
00:12:47,349 --> 00:12:49,310
Then I will save everyone except you

186
00:12:49,727 --> 00:12:52,688
But if you take even one more step closer

187
00:12:52,897 --> 00:12:54,815
One step of yours, one glance

188
00:12:54,899 --> 00:12:57,359
I will kill everyone
And bury them at your feet

189
00:12:58,861 --> 00:12:59,862
[SIGH]

190
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,531
Go ahead, General

191
00:13:05,826 --> 00:13:06,827
I

192
