I'm fine

193
00:13:12,416 --> 00:13:13,417
I am

194
00:13:16,128 --> 00:13:17,755
- Mama, I...
- I know

195
00:13:20,132 --> 00:13:22,009
I truly know

196
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:27,348
If this is the end
then this is also my fate

197
00:13:29,225 --> 00:13:30,476
So go

198
00:13:31,060 --> 00:13:34,355
(Kim Sun)
Do not stop and go to His Majesty, General

199
00:13:58,420 --> 00:13:59,380
It's a rebellion

200
00:13:59,463 --> 00:14:01,715
(Young Wang-yeo)
Do not let a single breath of that family survive

201
00:14:01,799 --> 00:14:02,883
