01:19:40,150 --> 01:19:41,193
[I BLOW WITH MY MOUTH]

1135
01:19:41,276 --> 01:19:43,403
[MEANINGFUL SOUND EFFECTS]

1136
01:19:55,957 --> 01:19:56,917
[JOYFUL BREATHING]

1137
01:19:57,000 --> 01:19:59,753
(Euntak)
I knew
I knew how to sing it

