[EUN-TAK BLOWS AIR THROUGH HER LIPS]

1158
01:20:53,765 --> 01:20:54,683
[APPLICATION SOUND EFFECT]

1159
01:20:57,561 --> 01:20:58,979
[EUN-TAK'S EXCITED BREATHING]

1160
01:20:59,729 --> 01:21:02,357
