01:21:16,955 --> 01:21:18,248
Did you catch me just now?

1165
01:21:20,333 --> 01:21:22,586
(Eun-tak)
Ah, I can't take it anymore, ah, it's hot

1166
01:21:22,669 --> 01:21:23,920
[EUNTAK BLOWS AIR THROUGH HER LIPS]

1167
01:21:24,004 --> 01:21:25,755
I thought it was cold because it was blue.

1168
01:21:27,924 --> 01:21:30,552
Originally, the temperature of the blue light
is the highest, you liberal arts student.

1169
01:21:30,635 --> 01:21:32,012
