1203
01:22:52,092 --> 01:22:53,760
You know I can see ghosts, right?

1204
01:22:53,843 --> 01:22:55,512
(Euntak)
Since the moment I was born

1205
01:22:57,722 --> 01:22:59,683
I was born with this, you know?

1206
01:22:59,766 --> 01:23:01,851
I think it's because of this
that the ghosts

1207
01:23:01,935 --> 01:23:03,520
