1208
01:23:03,728 --> 01:23:06,189
You see this? This

1209
01:23:11,820 --> 01:23:15,031
[SIGNIFICANT SOUND EFFECT]

1210
01:23:15,115 --> 01:23:16,074
[A FAINT MOAN]

