1233
01:24:16,926 --> 01:24:18,720
If what I see in you is all there is

1234
01:24:19,554 --> 01:24:20,972
Then you're not a goblin bride.

1235
01:24:21,765 --> 01:24:23,558
You have no utility value to the goblin.

1236
01:24:24,768 --> 01:24:26,519
(Kim Shin)
It’s unfortunate that I can’t see ghosts,

1237
01:24:26,603 --> 01:24:29,105
but since I'm living a life that’s essentially a bonus,
live gratefully.

1238
01:24:29,731 --> 01:24:31,274
You simply broke the rules

1239
01:24:31,357 --> 01:24:33,943
and got involved in human life and death,
causing side effects.

1240
01:24:39,074 --> 01:24:40,909
What if I don’t want to bear it?

1241
01:24:40,992 --> 01:24:42,786
There’s always the method of just dying as originally destined.

1242
01:24:42,869 --> 01:24:43,745
[AN ABSURD SOUND OF BREATH]

1243
01:24:43,912 --> 01:24:44,954
You really...

1244
01:24:49,375 --> 01:24:52,754
I got it;
let me ask that question again.

1245
01:24:52,837 --> 01:24:53,963
Sir, are you perhaps

1246
01:24:55,298 --> 01:24:56,883
- a goblin?
- No.

1247
01:24:56,966 --> 01:24:58,134
- No?
- No.

1248
01:24:58,218 --> 01:24:59,302
(Eun-tak)
Then what is it?

1249
01:25:00,720 --> 01:25:03,932
Why does an old man judge whether I have value or not?

1250
01:25:04,099 --> 01:25:05,683
You want to improve by at least 10 won, right?

1251
01:25:08,728 --> 01:25:11,731
(Kim-shin)
Someone who worries about a beggar-like situation
only by 10 won.

1252
01:25:15,568 --> 01:25:18,238
Live in reality, not in rumors.

1253
01:25:19,489 --> 01:25:21,116
You're not a goblin bride.

1254
01:25:23,159 --> 01:25:25,286
[A DISCONTENTED SIGH]

1255
01:25:28,832 --> 01:25:30,083
(Eun-tak)
Wait a minute
[Meaningful sound effect]

1256
01:25:34,170 --> 01:25:35,547
(Eun-tak)
That conversation isn't over yet...
[Kim-shin's surprised moan]

1257
01:25:35,630 --> 01:25:37,590
[LIVELY MUSIC]

1258
01:25:37,674 --> 01:25:38,591
[THE DOOR SLAMS SHUT]

1259
01:25:45,014 --> 01:25:48,560
(Kim Shin) Did you just come
through that door? Following me?

1260
01:25:49,352 --> 01:25:51,646
Oh, how did you get in?

1261
01:25:54,357 --> 01:25:56,651
You grabbed the handle

1262
01:25:56,860 --> 01:25:58,069
and followed Mr. Min...

1263
01:26:00,113 --> 01:26:01,489
But why is it like this here?

1264
01:26:01,573 --> 01:26:04,617
(Kim Shin) Hey, that's why I'm asking right
now. How did you pass through that door, anyway?

1265
01:26:04,701 --> 01:26:07,620
Oh, was it Paju? The
English village there?

1266
01:26:08,163 --> 01:26:10,373
(Eun Tak) Ugh, but even if
it was there, it's still strange.

1267
01:26:10,456 --> 01:26:13,585
What the heck is going
on? Where exactly are we?

1268
01:26:13,793 --> 01:26:14,794
Canada?

1269
01:26:15,003 --> 01:26:16,129
Is it Canada?

1270
01:26:17,964 --> 01:26:19,340
(Eun Tak) If it's Canada...

1271
01:26:20,383 --> 01:26:22,802
That, the land of maple leaves?

1272
01:26:23,136 --> 01:26:24,470
The one with the auroras?

1273
01:26:24,596 --> 01:26:26,890
(Euntak)
Is this really a foreign country?

1274
01:26:34,939 --> 01:26:37,775
Wow, Uncle, you had this ability too?

1275
01:26:38,401 --> 01:26:40,987
You have it too, what are you really?

1276
01:26:42,405 --> 01:26:45,742
(Euntak)
This is really Canada and
if Uncle's abilities are like this

1277
01:26:45,950 --> 01:26:47,160
I’ve made up my mind

1278
01:26:49,078 --> 01:26:50,747
- What?
- I’ve decided, I

1279
01:26:50,830 --> 01:26:51,706
(Kim Shin)
What, what?

1280
01:26:51,789 --> 01:26:53,416
I'm going to get married, to you, Uncle

1281
01:26:53,499 --> 01:26:56,794
(Euntak)
No matter how much I think about it
I really think you are a goblin

1282
01:26:57,295 --> 01:26:58,922
[smiling slightly]
I love you

1283
01:26:59,005 --> 01:27:01,382
[EMOTIONAL MUSIC]

1284
01:27:47,929 --> 01:27:50,765
(Euntak)
Is this it? A red carpet for me?

1285
01:27:51,516 --> 01:27:53,351
It’s an honor to walk together, right?

1286
01:27:55,103 --> 01:27:57,105
(Kim Shin)
What on earth are you talking about?

1287
01:27:57,188 --> 01:27:59,774
(Euntak)
I’m going to be your bride 200 years later

1288
01:28:01,901 --> 01:28:03,528
(Kim Shin)
It seems like you'll keep calling me

1289
01:28:03,611 --> 01:28:06,114
I want to appear intelligent and flawless anywhere, anytime

1290
01:28:06,614 --> 01:28:07,657
Did I seem manly?

1291
01:28:07,740 --> 01:28:09,367
- (Kim Shin) Deokhwa
- Is something bad happening?

1292
01:28:09,450 --> 01:28:11,077
Who says I’m going to be Uncle's bride?

1293
01:28:11,286 --> 01:28:14,622
(Fortune Teller)
Be careful of the man with the hat, the black hat.

1294
01:28:14,706 --> 01:28:17,375
(Euntak)
Am I going to die?
I'm only just nineteen?

1295
01:28:17,458 --> 01:28:20,378
I died at nine and I died at ten

1296
01:28:23,840 --> 01:28:24,966
That's death

1297
01:28:25,049 --> 01:28:27,302
[THUNDER CRASHES]

1298
01:28:28,845 --> 01:28:30,596
Subtitle: Choi Hyeran

